# MindfulNest — Firebase / server

## COPPA guard (spec §7.2)

- Any Cloud Function that imports `firebase-admin` and touches `/children/*` **must** import `withCoppaGuard`.
- Verify: `npm run test:coppa-contracts`

## Firestore rules

- After any change to `firestore/firestore.rules` or rules tests: `npm run test:rules`

## Region

- Cloud Functions v2: `us-central1` (LD-222 US data residency)

## App Check

- Client: `src/services/appCheckService.ts` — init before callables.
- Callables: `enforceAppCheck: true` (LD-802 gate closed 2026-05-25).
